properties.name: _Dakota Territory
properties.note:
Dakota Territory (1868-07-25)

1868/07/25 -> 1871/02/08

The small remnant of Dakota Territory in present Montana again became non-county area when Wyoming Territory boundaries were established.

(U.S. Stat., vol. 15, ch. 235[1868], secs. 1, 17/pp. 178, 183; Van Zandt, 136, 144)
